rental.description:
In an unbeatable location and only a short walk to public transport including the soon to be completed light rail, local schools, shops and a town centre growing on what seems like a daily basis.  This three bedroom, two bathroom, lock up car park,  simply must be at the top of your list of rental properties to inspect.

This impressive three-story townhouse presents an ideal opportunity to secure a low maintenance lifestyle of comfort and convenience. Downstairs boasts a separate outdoor area, fantastic functional kitchen with separate lounge and dining areas. There is also a separate toilet with wash basin on this level. Upstairs there is a large living area including balcony access and a main bedroom with ensuite and walk-in robe. On the top floor you are serviced by two bedrooms and large main bathroom with separate toilet and wash basin. Both bedrooms have spacious wardrobes.

And to top off this amazing property, there is a 5.4kw solar system present and you seek the benefit of the rebates from the grid. There is a huge saving with this and it is helped with double glazed windows throughout.

Features include:

- Spacious and light filled living and dining area both opening to a private courtyard;
- Sleek modern kitchen features stone bench-tops, gas cooking, dishwasher and fridge included;
- Separate living space on middle level with access to a secluded balcony;
- Three large bedrooms, main is complete with en-suite;
- Well appointed bathroom with a shower and bath;
- Separate Toilet downstairs with separate Laundry;
- Floorboards downstairs with quality blinds throughout;
- Swimming Pool in complex;
- Double glazed windows throughout;
- Beautiful views to pond and nature;
- Contemporary fa&#231;ade and common gardens offer street appeal;
- 5.4k/w Solar System with credits going back to tenant;
- Reverse cycle air conditioning and fresh neutral tones;
- 1.5 Car remote lock-up garage with large storage area, plenty of extra parking on the street;
- Close to schools, shops, transport and nearly completed light-rail;
- Easy access to the main arterial roads, minutes from the CBD.
- Available; 30th of April 2025
- EER not available;

This property complies with the ACT ceiling insulation standard

Inspection Guidelines:
(For www.canberrapropertypartners.com.au and www.allhomes.com.au only)
1. To schedule an inspection, simply click the &quot;BOOK INSPECTION&quot; button.
2. Register to attend an existing inspection.
3. If there&#39;s no scheduled time available, register anyway to ensure we can notify you once a time is arranged.
4. Failure to register means we won&#39;t be able to inform you of any changes, cancellations, or additional inspection times. Remember, inspections may be canceled if no registrations are received, so please ensure you register.

Pet Policy:
Per the Residential Tenancies Act Clause 71AE, tenants must submit a written request to the lessor for consent to keep pet(s) on the property. The lessor may impose conditions on this consent, such as specifying the number and type of animals permitted and any associated rectification costs.

Rent Options:
At Canberra Property Partners, we offer our tenants flexible rental payment options, including weekly, fortnightly, or monthly payments tailored to your pay cycle. Feel free to inquire for further details.

