This unit is HUGE with 90sq/m internal space, 27sq/m balcony and a 17sq/m courtyard, it must be one of the best and biggest two bedroom units going around. Centrally located and just a stroll to all the amenities the area has to offer, this delightful two-bedroom unit in the popular &#39;HUDSON SQUARE&#39; complex is sure to please.

As you enter the unit you are greeted with an open plan living/dining/kitchen area with plenty of space on offer. There is a huge covered outdoor balcony off this area that is ideal for a bbq and outdoor living. The kitchen is well positioned and its functional design includes induction cooktop, range hood, sink, dishwasher, electric oven, microwave space, excellent storage with plenty of bench space on the 20mm granite benchtop.

The large main bedroom suitably comes off the living/kitchen area. It has built in cupboards, plenty of natural light, and a well-proportioned ensuite. Access to the balcony is also available from this bedroom. The other bedroom is equipped with built in robes and can accommodate large bedroom furniture. This bedroom also has access onto a very large private courtyard via a sliding door.

The main bathroom is accommodated with a vanity and plenty of bench space, separate shower and toilet.

The laundry is neatly tucked away behind concealed doors.

The unit has beautiful carpets/floorboards and neutral paint tones throughout. The two allocated underground secure car spaces with storage cage is conveniently located under the complex accessed via lift. The Hudson Square complex also includes commercial space on the ground floor, landscaped gardens and plenty of external carpark space.

Other features the property includes is direct access to the nearly completed light rail, bus stop, caf&#233;’s, restaurants, medical centers, retail outlets and grocery shopping. It is also very close to licensed clubs, department stores, banks, schools, arterial roads and the list is endless.

Features:
- Main bedroom with robes, ensuite and balcony access;
- Large Bedroom with Built in Robes and courtyard access;
- Bathroom with vanity, shower, toilet;
- Concealed Laundry;
- Fantastic kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite benchtops;
- First floor unit;
- Reverse Cycle Air-conditioning;
- Huge covered spacious balcony (dual access);
- 2 Allocated car spaces under building with storage cage;
- Security intercom;
- Close to schools and transport;
- Walking distance to endless Amenities.
- EER: 6.0
This property is exempt from the ACT minimum ceiling standard.

- Available 25th of March 2025

