Luxurious home located in one of Canberra&#39;s most central suburbs, Wright (Molonglo Valley) which includes 5 bedrooms, 2 en-suites, rumpus, multiple living areas, bathroom, alfresco, double garage along with extra car space on driveway, functional backyard, and only a few metres to Link Park and Link Park Outdoor Fitness Station.

Complementing the convenience of the location, the property is only few minutes walk to the primary school, childcare centre, chemist, 24/7 Club Lime Fitness Centre, Coombs shops, Stromlo Forest Park and Stromlo Forest Memorial.

The fantastic location of this property offers approximately 10-15 minutes drive to Canberra City Centre, ANU, Belconnen, Barton, Woden and moments to Cooleman Court Shops, 

Key features of this family sized home:
- 5 bedrooms, all with built-in robes, ceiling fans and segregated from other bedrooms;
- Master bedroom with ensuite and walk in robe;
- 2 Ensuites and main bathroom with all amenities;
- All Bedrooms have hardwood floor boards;
- Tiled floors in living areas;
- Rumpus area which can also be used as a study room/library;
- Large living and dining area and access to Alfresco;
- Contemporary Kitchen with stone bench top, dishwasher, oven and griller, gas cooking, microwave and walk in butlers pantry;
- Kitchen was huge storage and well positioned next to dining area;
- Butlers pantry also has gas cooking and range-hood;
- Alfresco with access to landscaped backyard;
- Large linen cupboards and plenty of storage cupboards;
- Stylish modern interiors and convenient living;
- Quality blinds and flooring (no carpet);
- Landscaped outdoor living;
- Double lock up garage with remote door and internal access;
- Car space on driveway;
- Ducted heating and fridgerated cooling throughout;
- Inslab heating in living areas and bathrooms;
- Ducted Vacuum;
- Enclosed backyard with storage shed;
- Playgrounds and parks in walking distance perfect for kids to burn off steam;
- NBN for faster internet;
- Wright is one of few self-contained suburbs in Canberra close to modern primary school, childcare centre, multiple parks, playgrounds and riverside entertaining areas;
- Close to arterial roads;
