Stylish, chic and contemporary, this as new light filled apartment is perfectly positioned to make the most of the lifestyle on offer at your doorstep. Take a short stroll to the hip new dining venues and bars that are popping up around the city, or pop on down to picturesque Lake Burley Griffin for a leisurely stroll. Stunning ever changing views with the seasons over the lake and Glebe Park will have you mesmerised, and you will enjoy a box seat position for the annual Skyfire fireworks display.
Featuring a generous sized bedroom, with panoramic windows to take in the views, and a luxe bathroom. The spacious kitchen features an abundance of bench space and storage, and overlooks the large living area and enclosed balcony, perfect for entertaining with friends and family. Take advantage of the numerous facilities that are on offer at Metropol, including roof top entertaining terraces and pool area.

